      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1780053061467,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. Now say SR2 wants to conduct a meeting in which he wants to include \n    manager under him and sr3 \n    he will send a ping to all of these guys thus getting a message  on the application \n    and also a mail of their emial \n\n    the same can be said of messages on the app \n    say m1 sends msg to two of this employes they will get a notificarion on\n    their portal  ",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Now say SR2 wants to conduct a meeting in which he wants to include \n    manager under him and sr3 \n    he will send a ping to all of these guys thus getting a message  on the application \n    and also a mail of their emial \n\n    the same can be said of messages on the app \n    say m1 sends msg to two of this employes they will get a notificarion on\n    their portal  ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
